KNOW US
Malabar Group is a trusted property management company based in Guelph, Ontario since 2020. We take care of different types of properties, like houses, apartments, and commercial spaces. Our team handles repairs, maintenance, and day-to-day tasks to keep everything in good shape. We work hard to make sure property owners feel supported and tenants are happy. We're here to solve problems quickly and keep things running smoothly.
Our goal is to take the stress out of managing properties. Malabar Group offers friendly and professional service you can count on. We care about building strong relationships with our clients. Choose us for simple, dependable property management.
WHAT WE HAVE
We provide a wide range of services, including PROPERTY rentals, ensuring reliable and affordable transportation solutions. Our car wash service delivers top-quality cleaning for a spotless finish. We also offer gardening services to enhance outdoor spaces, along with fencing solutions for security and privacy, ensuring a well-maintained property.
We offer reliable and affordable property rentals for residential and commercial needs.
